      • AbstractID

        public AbstractID(AbstractID id)
        Creates a new abstract ID from the given one.

        The given and the newly created abstract ID will be identical, i.e. a comparison by equals will return true and both objects will have the same hash code.

        Parameters:
        id - the abstract ID to copy
